name: PROTOBUNNYFINAL
description:
ProtoBunny:  A visual novel by Jason Jackson, Mitchell Kushpa, Erick Melo, and TJ Karl.  

Emily has just received a new video game from her Dad, but it appears to be displaying some strange behavior. Something feels all too familiar about this game, but what could it be? Emily has never even heard of this game before, so how can it be familiar?  Play through three alternate endings and resolve the mystery that is PROTOBUNNY.
